description: Following a mysterious message BUMBLEBEE returns to Earth with unlikely companions to face a new Decepticon threat.
name: Pilot (Part 1)

description: Bumblebee and his new allies struggle to find a teamwork dynamic as they protect Crown City from metal-devouring Underbite.
name: Pilot (Part 2)

description: Bumblebee's new troop needs to hone their teamwork, but they'll have to do it on the fly as they face off against two more Decepticon fugitives - Sharkticon HAMMERSTRIKE and wolf-like STEELJAW.
name: Trust Exercises

description: As Russell nervously tries befriending the neighborhood kids, Fixit - craving the action of a field assignment - gets in way over his head.
name: More than Meets the Eye

description: Beleaguered Bumblebee must learn to lead in his own way as the Team struggles to bring in a brutish Decepticon whose stasis pod has been discovered by human authorities.
name: W.W.O.D.?

description: Sideswipe's loyalty to the team comes into question as he and Bumblebee track down a Cybertronian crime-boss.
name: As the Kospego Commands!

description: As Denny and Russell work to stave off a greedy memorabilia-collector, Bee and his Team chase a collector of their own - a Decepticon with an impulsive urge to hoard all things "shiny."
name: Collect 'Em All

description: When Grimlock suddenly starts attacking his teammates, Bee must figure out why the stalwart Dinobot has turned from friend to foe.
name: True Colors

description: While Strongarm's first "solo" mission is marred by an over-protective Bumblebee, Denny's and Fixit's rivalry comes to a head.
name: Rumble in the Jungle

description: The Bee Team welcomes a visiting Autobot veteran just in time to fend off a Decepticon fugitive bent on monopolizing one of the Bot's most precious commodities.
name: Can You Dig It?

description: While in pursuit of a rebellious Decepticon, Bumblebee is exposed to a toxin that impacts his maturity, leaving the rest of the Bee Team to deal with both an escaped fugitive and a hyperactive leader.
name: Adventures in Bumblebee-Sitting!

description: When two rival Bounty Hunters land on earth, Bumblebee discovers that there's a price on his head.
name: Hunting Season

description: Sideswipe blackmails Strongarm into doing all of his chores while the Team tries to capture another slippery 'Con before the fugitive holes-up with Steeljaw's crew.

description: AL SAH-HIM TAKES HIS FINAL STEPS TO ASCENSION; ROY AND THEA REUNITE — Oliver/Al Sah-him (Stephen Amell) finishes his training and is left with two final tasks to become the next Ra’s al Ghul. Ra’s (guest star Matt Nable) threatens Nyssa (guest star Katrina Law) and delivers some shocking news. Meanwhile, Malcolm (John Barrowman) makes a surprising offer to Team Arrow and Thea (Willa Holland) goes to see Roy (Colton Haynes).
name: This is Your Sword

description: When Homer gets an old film roll developed, the family takes a trip down memory lane to see the origins of how Bart and Lisa first started fighting with each other.
name: The Kids Are All Fight

description: As Wells (Tom Cavanagh) once again gets the upper hand on the S.T.A.R. Labs team, Barry (Grant Gustin) realizes he needs to make a big move and reaches out to an old foe, Captain Cold (guest-star Wentworth Miller), for help. Joe (Jesse L. Martin) and Caitlin (Danielle Panabaker) warn Barry that Cold can't be trusted. True to form, Cold has his own agenda that involves the meta-humans trapped in the containment cells. As things seem to be going from bad to worse, The Flash gets reinforcements -- Arrow (guest star Stephen Amell) and Firestorm (guest star Robbie Amell).
name: Rogue Air

description: A group of teens gets a scare when a disheveled young pregnant woman approaches them muttering for help. Unfortunately, the woman doesn't survive but her baby does. Liv (Rose McIver) and Clive (Malcolm Goodwin) begin questioning suspects in her murder, and after consuming the victim's brain, a fierce maternal instinct kicks in for Liv. Meanwhile, Major (Robert Buckley) makes a shocking discovery.
name: Maternity Liv

description: When Raven chooses to hang out with Rose Wilson, a cool escaped criminal, the other Titans feel left out. To feel 'less lame,' they decide to go to Cool School.
name: Cool School

description: Robin teaches the Titans how to play soccer. They quickly become obsessed, and accidentally uncover the secret reason why the sport is so popular.
name: Kicking A Ball & Pretending To Be Hurt

description: After a chilling dream encounter, Finn and Jake are determined to reconnect with their reclusive brother.
name: Jermaine

description: BMO's favorite entertainers unexpectedly find a new home at the tree house.
name: Chips and Ice Cream

description: Peter befriends a group of mean girls after his feelings are hurt when his so-called friends decide to "roast" him.
name: Roasted Guy

description: Peter claims he would beat Liam Neeson (guest-voice Liam Neeson) in a fight, but when he is put to the test, he learns that winning is tougher than it seems. Meanwhile, Stewie becomes jealous when Lois decides to be a class mom and starts paying more attention to the other kids over him.
name: Fighting Irish
